title: Largest Ecuadorian-American population groups in the U.S. , by county 2010
summary: The Largest Ecuadorian-American Population in the groups U.S. was Population Hudson_County_NJ , who made 98512 number .
The most Ecuadorian-American Population was Bronx_County_NY , with just 17638 number .

In second place was Population Kings_County_NJ with 28684 number ; third place went to Population Queens_County_NY with 98512 number ; fourth place went to Population Suffolk_County_NY with 17638 number and fifth place went to Population Essex_County_NJ , who was 25169 number .
gold: This statistic depicts the largest Ecuadorian-American population groups living in different counties across the United States as of 2010 . At this time there were 98,512 people of Ecuadorian origin living in Queens County in New York .
